(2023, 01, ' The average american tosses 300 pounds of food each year, making food the number one contributor to America’s landfills. Eat your leftovers and keep your perishables in the fridge – the Earth is counting on it. Disponível em: https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net. Acesso em: 29 out. 2021 (adaptado). Esse cartaz de campanha sugere que 

